description:
Raymundo makes his attempt at running 18 MPH to win $200. Bobby got a text from a number he didn't recognize and the person said it was Latrell Sprewell. Bobby thinks he's getting catfished, again. Plus, a listener admits she's been having fake Zoom meetings to get away from her family for a bit!
